title: Crop Report for the Period October 13 to 19, 2015 (Government of Saskatchewan)
text: ( Source : Government of Saskatchewan ) Released on October 22 , 2015 Harvest is virtually complete in the province as 97 per cent of the crop is now in the bin, up from 91 per cent last week, according to Saskatchewan Agriculture's Weekly Crop
